profile.longBusinessSummary: Tastemaker Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus on companies in the restaurant, hospitality, and related technology and services sectors. Tastemaker Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2020 and is based in New York, New York.
